title: Adding link for vignette
body: Vignette on the front-page README currently doesn't link anywhere.

title: Development - small addition to the vignette
body: Updated the broken link to the vignette and added how allocate more memory to the JVM when corpora are to large to fit into the standard allocation to the JVM. Only changes in the vignette and README.

title: Enforce character document IDs on import
body: When `id.array` is not character e.g. `id.array=1:1000` in the `mallet.import` function then the `addInstances` call fails in a way that's really hard to diagnose.
